list.abstract: entire（英 [ɪnˈtaɪə]，美 [ɪnˈtaɪər]），英语单词，作形容词为全部的；整个的；完全的。作名词为未经阉割的公马；种马。短语搭配有entire life（整个生活）。例句为“The entire European coastline will be submerged.（整个欧洲海岸线将被淹没。）” entire相关近义词有overall、all等。副词形式entirely，名词形式entirety。

yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，谢谢你们替我想好了我整个的人生，但这是我人生中最糟糕的一部分。好了，我们走吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Our entire order is predicated on four dumplings and four entrees divided amongst four people. So, we'll just order three entrees.

yingyinNormal.en: Was it in your possession the entire time?

yingyinNormal.en: Gorg family. It is entire next generation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 格尔族系，他们的整个新生代。

yingyinNormal.en: Your invite has been sent to entire galaxy!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的邀请函已经发送个全星系了！

yingyinNormal.en: Yours for the entire trip. Four new Maybachs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 您全程的交通工具，四辆全新的迈巴赫。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm gonna go out and embrace that entire crowd.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要出去接纳那群人。

yingyinNormal.en: He's got more ammunition than the entire us army.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他身上带的弹药，比一整支军队还要多。

yingyinNormal.en: I have never been thus treated in my entire life!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我一辈子都没有被这样对待过！

yingyinNormal.en: What? Refuse to play? I've killed an entire species!
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么，拒绝参加？我灭绝了整个虫族。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a ledger. The Syndicate's entire infrastructure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是个账册，存储了辛迪加的所有机密。

yingyinNormal.en: Pheebs, I have studied evolution my entire adult life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 菲比，我整个成年都在研究进化论。

yingyinNormal.en: The ancient models give the entire endeavor a bad name.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些旧型号复制人让我们的复制人制造计划背上骂名。

yingyinNormal.en: Damon and I spent the entire summer looking for Stefan.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我和达蒙整个夏天都在找斯特凡。

yingyinNormal.en: That's the only truly remarkable aspect of the entire affair.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是整个过程中最非凡的部分。

yingyinNormal.en: The entire institution of gift-giving makes no sense. Too late.
yingyinNormal.zh: 整个送礼物的机制是没有意义的。太迟了。

yingyinNormal.en: You claim you were with Mr. Sweeney the entire time? No, not the entire time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你声称一直都跟斯威尼先生在一起？不，不是一直在一起。

yingyinNormal.en: I spent the entire day with you, why didn't you tell me?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我一整天都和你在一起，你为何没告诉我？

yingyinNormal.en: Who? Oh, just my parents and my entire family. What? Why?
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁？就我爸妈，和我全家人。什么？为什么？

yingyinNormal.en: It wasn't easy getting the entire uniform, but done and done.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把所有的制服都拿来的确很难，但... 说到做到。
